00368         get { if (!cache[0]) FetchConvoIdFromRuntime(); return cache_convo_id; }
00369     }
00370     
00371     internal void FetchConvoIdFromRuntime()
00372     {
00373         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Fetching P_CONVO_ID from runtime");
00374         skypeRef.transport.SubmitPropertyRequest(19, 930, this.OID);
00375         if (skypeRef.transport.PropResponseWasOk(930))
00376         {
00377             cache_convo_id = (SktConversation)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeObject(18); // SktConversation class ID = 18
00378             cache[0] = true;
00379         }
00380         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromPropRequest();
00381     }

01048     public SktVideo.List GetLiveSessionVideos ()
01049     {
01050         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing Participant.GetLiveSessionVideos");
01051         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 145, OID);
01052         SktVideo.List videos = new SktVideo.List(); // We always guarantee non-null list is returned
01053         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
01054         int argNr, marker;
01055         do
01056         {
01057             marker = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
01058             if (marker != 'z')
01059             {
01060                 if (marker == 'N') skypeRef.Error("SktParticipant.GetLiveSessionVideos failed.");
01061                 argNr = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
01062                 switch (argNr)
01063                 {
01064                     case 1:
01065                         videos = (SktVideo.List)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeObjectList(11);
01066                         break;
01067                     case 'z': marker = argNr; break; // exiting the arg loop if the method failed
01068                     default:
01069                         skypeRef.Error(String.Format("Got unexpected response argument {0} from runtime in SktParticipant.GetLiveSessionVideos", argNr));
01070                         break;
01071                 }
01072             }
01073         } while (marker != 'z');
01074         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromMethod();
01075         return videos;
01076     } // SktParticipant.GetLiveSessionVideos
01077     
01078     internal override void DispatchEvent (uint eventId)
01079     {
01080         switch (eventId)
01081         {
01082             case 1:
01083                 skypeRef.events.ProcessOnParticipantIncomingDTMF(this);
01084                 break;
01085             case 146:
01086                 skypeRef.events.ProcessOnParticipantLiveSessionVideosChanged(this);
01087                 break;
01088             default:
01089                 skypeRef.Error(String.Format("Invalid event ID {0} received for class Participant", eventId)); break;
01090         }
01091     }

01332     public override Boolean CheckVersion()
01333     {
01334         String runtimeVersion = "";
01335         runtimeVersion = GetVersionString();
01336         string[] sections = runtimeVersion.Split('/');
01337         Boolean ok = sections[0].Equals(SupportedRuntimeVersion);
01338         if (!ok) { Log(String.Format("WARNING! Runtime version {0} and supported runtime version ({1})mismatch", sections[0], SupportedRuntimeVersion)); }
01339         return ok;
01340     }

01637     internal override SktObject CreateObject(uint classId, uint objectId)
01638     {
01639         SktObject newObject;
01640         switch (classId)
01641         {
01642             case  19 : newObject = NewParticipant(objectId, this); break;
01643             case  10 : newObject = NewContactGroup(objectId, this); break;
01644             case  11 : newObject = NewVideo(objectId, this); break;
01645             case   9 : newObject = NewMessage(objectId, this); break;
01646             case   7 : newObject = NewVoicemail(objectId, this); break;
01647             case   6 : newObject = NewTransfer(objectId, this); break;
01648             case   2 : newObject = NewContact(objectId, this); break;
01649             case  18 : newObject = NewConversation(objectId, this); break;
01650             case   1 : newObject = NewContactSearch(objectId, this); break;
01651             case  12 : newObject = NewSms(objectId, this); break;
01652             case   5 : newObject = NewAccount(objectId, this); break;

04356     public SktContact.List GetContacts ()
04357     {
04358         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing ContactGroup.GetContacts");
04359         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 8, OID);
04360         SktContact.List contacts = new SktContact.List(); // We always guarantee non-null list is returned
04361         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
04362         int argNr, marker;
04363         do
04364         {
04365             marker = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
04366             if (marker != 'z')
04367             {
04368                 if (marker == 'N') skypeRef.Error("SktContactGroup.GetContacts failed.");
04369                 argNr = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
04370                 switch (argNr)
04371                 {
04372                     case 1:
04373                         contacts = (SktContact.List)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeObjectList(2);
04374                         break;
04375                     case 'z': marker = argNr; break; // exiting the arg loop if the method failed
04376                     default:
04377                         skypeRef.Error(String.Format("Got unexpected response argument {0} from runtime in SktContactGroup.GetContacts", argNr));
04378                         break;
04379                 }
04380             }
04381         } while (marker != 'z');
04382         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromMethod();
04383         return contacts;
04384     } // SktContactGroup.GetContacts

04554     internal override void DispatchPropertyUpdate (uint propId, object value, bool hasValue)
04555     {
04556         switch (propId)
04557         {
04558             case 130: /* Video.P_STATUS */
04559                 cache[0] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04560                 if (hasValue)
04561                 {
04562                     cache_status = (SktVideo.STATUS)value;
04563                     if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_STATUS = " + cache_status.ToString());
04564                 }
04565                 else if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_STATUS - update without value");
04566                 skypeRef.events.FireOnVideoStatus(this, cache_status);
04567                 break;
04568                 
04569             case 131: /* Video.P_ERROR */
04570                 cache[1] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04571                 if (hasValue)
04572                 {
04573                     cache_error = (String)value;
04574                     if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_ERROR = " + cache_error.ToString());
04575                 }
04576                 else if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_ERROR - update without value");
04577                 skypeRef.events.FireOnVideoError(this, cache_error);
04578                 break;
04579                 
04580             case 132: /* Video.P_DEBUGINFO */
04581                 cache[2] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04582                 if (hasValue)
04583                 {
04584                     cache_debuginfo = (String)value;
04585                     if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_DEBUGINFO = " + cache_debuginfo.ToString());
04586                 }
04587                 else if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_DEBUGINFO - update without value");
04588                 skypeRef.events.FireOnVideoDebuginfo(this, cache_debuginfo);
04589                 break;
04590                 
04591             case 133: /* Video.P_DIMENSIONS */
04592                 cache[3] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04593                 if (hasValue)
04594                 {
04595                     cache_dimensions = (String)value;
04596                     if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_DIMENSIONS = " + cache_dimensions.ToString());
04597                 }
04598                 else if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Video.P_DIMENSIONS - update without value");
04599                 skypeRef.events.FireOnVideoDimensions(this, cache_dimensions);
04600                 break;
04601                 
04602             case 134: /* Video.P_MEDIA_TYPE */
04603                 cache[4] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04604                 if (hasValue)
04605                 {
04606                     cache_media_type = (SktVideo.MEDIATYPE)value;

04610                 skypeRef.events.FireOnVideoMediaType(this, cache_media_type);
04611                 break;
04612                 
04613             case 1104: /* Video.P_CONVO_ID */
04614                 cache[5] = hasValue; // if no value - invalidate cache
04615                 if (hasValue)

04617                     cache_convo_id = null;

06826         switch (propId)

06831                 {
06832                     cache_type = (SktTransfer.TYPE)value;
06833                     if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Transfer.P_TYPE = " + cache_type.ToString());
06834                 }
06835                 else if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Transfer.P_TYPE - update without value");
06836                 skypeRef.events.FireOnTransferType(this, cache_type);
06837                 break;

06839             case 81: /* Transfer.P_PARTNER_HANDLE */

07396     /* SktTransfer class methods */
07397     
07407     public Boolean Accept (String filenameWithPath)
07408     {
07409         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing Transfer.Accept");
07410         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 3, OID);
07411         skypeRef.encoder.AddFileNameParam(1, filenameWithPath);
07412         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
07413         Dictionary<uint, uint> tagMap = new Dictionary<uint, uint> { {1, 1} };
07414         object[] args = new object[1];
07415         args[0] = false;
07416         skypeRef.decoder.DecodeMethodResponseArguments(1, ref args, new uint[1]{0}, ref tagMap, "SktTransfer.Accept");
07417         return (Boolean)args[0];
07418     }
07419     
07424     public void Pause ()
07425     {
07426         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing Transfer.Pause");
07427         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 4, OID);
07428         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
07429         skypeRef.decoder.DecodeMethodResponseWithNoArguments("SktTransfer.Pause");
07430     }
07431     
07434     public void Resume ()
07435     {
07436         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing Transfer.Resume");
07437         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 5, OID);
07438         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
07439         skypeRef.decoder.DecodeMethodResponseWithNoArguments("SktTransfer.Resume");
07440     }
07441

08063         get { if (!cache[0]) FetchTypeFromRuntime(); return cache_type; }
08064     }

08066     internal void FetchTypeFromRuntime()
08067     {
08068         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Fetching P_TYPE from runtime");
08069         skypeRef.transport.SubmitPropertyRequest(2, 202, this.OID);
08070         if (skypeRef.transport.PropResponseWasOk(202))
08071         {
08072             cache_type = (SktContact.TYPE)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeUint();
08073             cache[0] = true;
08074         }
08075         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromPropRequest();
08076     }

11868     public SktContact.List GetResults (uint from=0, uint count=uint.MaxValue)
11869     {
11870         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing ContactSearch.GetResults");
11871         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 11, OID);
11872         skypeRef.encoder.AddUintParam(1, from);
11873         skypeRef.encoder.AddUintParam(2, count);
11874         SktContact.List contacts = new SktContact.List(); // We always guarantee non-null list is returned
11875         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
11876         int argNr, marker;
11877         do
11878         {
11879             marker = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
11880             if (marker != 'z')
11881             {
11882                 if (marker == 'N') skypeRef.Error("SktContactSearch.GetResults failed.");
11883                 argNr = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
11884                 switch (argNr)
11885                 {
11886                     case 1:
11887                         contacts = (SktContact.List)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeObjectList(2);
11888                         break;
11889                     case 'z': marker = argNr; break; // exiting the arg loop if the method failed
11890                     default:
11891                         skypeRef.Error(String.Format("Got unexpected response argument {0} from runtime in SktContactSearch.GetResults", argNr));
11892                         break;
11893                 }
11894             }
11895         } while (marker != 'z');
11896         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromMethod();
11897         return contacts;
11898     } // SktContactSearch.GetResults

12657     public void SetBody (
12658         out SktSms.SETBODYRESULT result,
12659         out List<String> chunks,
12660         out uint    charsUntilNextChunk,
12661         String      text)
12662     {
12663         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Executing Sms.SetBody");
12664         uint RequestId = skypeRef.encoder.AddMethodHeader(ClassId, 7, OID);
12665         skypeRef.encoder.AddStringParam(1, text);
12666         result = 0;
12667         chunks = new List<String>(); // We always guarantee non-null list is returned
12668         charsUntilNextChunk = 0;
12669         skypeRef.transport.SubmitMethodRequest (RequestId);
12670         int argNr, marker;
12671         do
12672         {
12673             marker = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
12674             if (marker != 'z')
12675             {
12676                 if (marker == 'N') skypeRef.Error("SktSms.SetBody failed.");
12677                 argNr = (char)skypeRef.transport.ReadByte();
12678                 switch (argNr)
12679                 {
12680                     case 1:
12681                         result = (SktSms.SETBODYRESULT)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeInt();
12682                         break;
12683                     case 2:
12684                         chunks = skypeRef.decoder.DecodeStringList();
12685                         break;
12686                     case 3:
12687                         charsUntilNextChunk = skypeRef.decoder.DecodeUint();
12688                         break;
12689                     case 'z': marker = argNr; break; // exiting the arg loop if the method failed
12690                     default:
12691                         skypeRef.Error(String.Format("Got unexpected response argument {0} from runtime in SktSms.SetBody", argNr));
12692                         break;
12693                 }
12694             }
12695         } while (marker != 'z');
12696         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromMethod();
12697     } // SktSms.SetBody

13415     public SktAccount.STATUS P_STATUS
13416     {
13417         get { if (!cache[0]) FetchStatusFromRuntime(); return cache_status; }
13418     }
13419     
13420     internal void FetchStatusFromRuntime()
13421     {
13422         if (skypeRef.logging) skypeRef.Log("Fetching P_STATUS from runtime");
13423         skypeRef.transport.SubmitPropertyRequest(5, 70, this.OID);
13424         if (skypeRef.transport.PropResponseWasOk(70))
13425         {
13426             cache_status = (SktAccount.STATUS)skypeRef.decoder.DecodeUint();
13427             cache[0] = true;
13428         }
13429         skypeRef.transport.ResumeSocketReaderFromPropRequest();
13430     }

15040 
15053 public class SktEvents : SktEventsBase
15054 {
15055     public SktEvents (Form form, SktSkype skype) : base(form, skype) {}
15056     
15057     
15058     public class OnParticipantConvoIdArgs : EventArgs
15059     {
15060         public SktParticipant sender;
15061         public SktConversation value;
15062         public OnParticipantConvoIdArgs(SktParticipant sender, SktConversation newValue) { this.sender = sender;  value = newValue; }
15063     }
15064     
15065     public event OnParticipantConvoIdHandler OnParticipantConvoId;    
15066     public delegate void OnParticipantConvoIdHandler (SktParticipant sender, OnParticipantConvoIdArgs e);
15067     
15068     internal void OnParticipantConvoIdInNewThread(object o)
15069     {
15070         OnParticipantConvoIdArgs e = (OnParticipantConvoIdArgs)o;
15071         OnParticipantConvoId(e.sender, e);
15072     }
15073     
15074     internal void FireOnParticipantConvoId(SktParticipant sender, SktConversation value)
15075     {
15076         if (OnParticipantConvoId == null) return; // Event not assigned    
15077         OnParticipantConvoIdArgs args = new OnParticipantConvoIdArgs(sender, value);    
15078         if (gui == null) { FireCallbackInSeparateThread(args, OnParticipantConvoIdInNewThread); return; } // No gui firing in separate thread
15079         gui.BeginInvoke(OnParticipantConvoId, new object[] { sender, args }); // Syncing to GUI thread
15080     }    
15081     
15082     
15083     public class OnParticipantIdentityArgs : EventArgs
15084     {
15085         public SktParticipant sender;
15086         public String value;
15087         public OnParticipantIdentityArgs(SktParticipant sender, String newValue) { this.sender = sender;  value = newValue; }
15088     }
15089     
15090     public event OnParticipantIdentityHandler OnParticipantIdentity;    
15091     public delegate void OnParticipantIdentityHandler (SktParticipant sender, OnParticipantIdentityArgs e);
15092     
15093     internal void OnParticipantIdentityInNewThread(object o)
15094     {
15095         OnParticipantIdentityArgs e = (OnParticipantIdentityArgs)o;
15096         OnParticipantIdentity(e.sender, e);
15097     }
15098     
15099     internal void FireOnParticipantIdentity(SktParticipant sender, String value)

19841     internal void ProcessOnConversationParticipantListChange (SktConversation sender)
19842     {
